summary: Pepper[[MORE]] Name: Pepper Cherrywood Age: 10th Grade Sex: Female Birth Date: June / Gemini   Pepper is very Shy, timid tomboy...
caption:
Pepper

Name: Pepper Cherrywood

Age: 10th Grade

Sex: Female

Birth Date: June / Gemini 


Pepper is very Shy, timid tomboy and is short. She isn’t very good at talking to people. She is very cautious and is unsure of herself. She is a animal lover.

Her favorite season is winter.

She loves cats but is allergic to them.

She likes the night and is a night owl. 

Her favorite color is green. 

She often have a bored face but is actually, maybe happy. 

She can be sarcastic  

She likes any kind of music except for country music.

She likes romantic and Horror Movies

Her type is someone who understands and is easy to talk to/Outgoing.
